<h2 class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Everest Base Camp Trek Itinerary</h2>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 1 :&nbsp;Kathmandu to Lukla</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Take a flight to from Tribhuvan airport on Kathmandu to Lukla(2651 m / 8697ft) which takes around 4 hrs. Enjoy the stunning aerial&nbsp; view of mountains and geographical structure.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 2 :&nbsp;Lukla to Namche Bazar(Namche â€“ 3440 m / 11286 ft)</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Hike to Namche Bazar which may take about 5 to 6 hrs.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 3 :Namche Bazar&nbsp;</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Acclimatization Day in Namche&nbsp;</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 4 :&nbsp; Namche Bazar to Tengboche(Tengboche â€“ 3956 m / 12979 ft)</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Hike from Namche bazar to Tengboche through woods and rhodhodendron forest&nbsp;which takes around 5 to 6 hrs.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 5 :&nbsp;Tengboche to Dingboche(Dingboche â€“ 4380 m / 14370 ft&nbsp;)</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hike from Tengboche to Dingboche crossing bridges and rivers with sweeping views of the mountains&nbsp;which takes around 5 to 6 hrs.&nbsp;</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 6 :&nbsp;Dingboche</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Acclimatization day in Dingboche.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 7 :&nbsp;Dingboche to Lobuche(Lobuche â€“ 4938 m / 16200 ft)</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Hike from Dingboche to Lobuche through alpine meadows and summer yak pastures towards the end of the moraine of the Khumbu Glacier&nbsp;which takes around 4 to 5 hrs.&nbsp;</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 8 :&nbsp;Lobuche to Gorakshep (Pheriche â€“ 4371 m / 14340 ft â€“ 8 to 9 hrs)</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Cross the Changri Glacier to Gorakshep, and enjoy the highlight of reaching the Everest Base Camp.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 9 :&nbsp;Gorakshep to Pheriche&nbsp;(Pheriche â€“ 4371 m / 14340 ft â€“ 8 to 9 hrs)</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Treak to Kala Pathar in the morning for stunning sunrise views of Everest and surrounding vistas. Later descend to Periche.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 10 :&nbsp;Pheriche to Namche Bazar&nbsp;(Namche â€“ 3440 m / 11286 ft â€“ 6 to 7 hrs)</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Descend through Pangboche, with its great gompa, to Kyangjuma to Namche.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 11 :&nbsp;&nbsp;Namche Bazar to Lukla&nbsp;( Lukla&nbsp;â€“&nbsp;2651 m / 8697ft)</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Finally Descend down to Lukla.</p>



<p class="has-vivid-cyan-blue-color has-text-color">Day 12 :&nbsp;Lukla to Kathmandu</p>



<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Catch the flight back to Kathmandu.</p>
